articles.title: UltraTech to invest Rs 13,000 cr to add production capacity by 21.9 MTPA - Business Standard
articles.description: Cement maker UltraTech on Saturday announced a fresh investment of Rs 13,000 crore to add production capacity by 21.9 million tonnes per annum in the third phase of the growth, taking its total capacity to 182 MTPA after completion.
articles.content: UltraTech Cement is the third largest Cement producer in the world, outside of China, with a consolidated grey cement capacity of 137.85 MTPA
